  "Description": {
    "English": "A technology module harvested from the remains of an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">abandoned freighter</span> found floating in space. May also be salvaged during <span class=\"name name-stellar\">frigate expeditions</span>.<br><br>Pre-packed nano-expanders fill out this portable unit and graft it to an existing freighter, increasing its <span class=\"name name-stellar\">inventory capacity</span>. Apply at your freighter's <span class=\"name name-technology\">Upgrade Terminal</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从飘浮在太空中的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">废弃货船</span>残骸里采集出来的技术模块。还可在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰远征</span>过程中回收。<br><br>预装的纳米扩张器充斥着这个便携单位，将其移植到现有货船上后，即可增加其<span class=\"name name-stellar\">库存容量</span>。在货船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升级终端</span>上应用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從太空中漂浮的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">廢棄貨船</span>殘骸採收的科技模組，也可以在進行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡防艦探險</span>時回收獲得。<br><br>內含奈米擴充填料，平時體積小便利攜帶，使用時擴大至正常大小，即可接合在現有貨船上，提升貨船的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">道具欄容量</span>。可在貨船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升級終端站</span>套用。"
  },
